{
  "stem": "1042.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I came to Brnenec, so I start right away on the machines what he had there prepared.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Beside this, I had the machines what I took from Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And other three, four friends, what they knew also, the-- the-- the mechanical work, we start to put on the machines on the right spot, because we're supposed there to build, you know, to make the rockets, what we throw-- you know, the round one.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The grenades-- mixing up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We supposed to produce grenades.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But the machines what Schindler had prepared, they were not in good condition, and they were so huge, so big, we couldn't move with them, you know?",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we were working very hard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Even sometimes he told us, slow down a little bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's time.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You will do it a little bit later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I see, and whenever he had a chance, you know, he was coming through and throwing cigarettes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He just put one cigarette and throw it away.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Again, in a second, the other cigarette.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could throw 50, 60 cigarettes, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The people should pick up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They shall have a cigarette.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They did it, you know, special, because he behaved like a father there to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every move, he figured out, you know, how to do it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when we had a problem with the machines, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and I had to look-- they were-- part of machines, they were prepared to work, and they were working on it, but we couldn't make, you know, the amount what we supposed to.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So after two months, you know, the Gestapo from Krakow send him a letter.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was very close with him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If he wanted to, we-- we shall know something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were five people.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
